---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"

const title = "Privacy Policy"
const description = ""
---
<Layout {title} {description}>
    <div class="py-30 px-4 bg-white min-h-screen">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
            <div class="flex justify-between gap-10 mb-10">
                <div>
                    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-7 text-gray-800">Privacy Policy</h1>
                    <p class="text-gray-800"><b>Effective Date:</b> Aug 20, 2025</p>
                </div>
                <a href="/" class="mt-2">
                    <svg class="w-15" viewBox="0 0 746 764" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path d="M222.805 644.772L186.274 108.881L704.5 451.158L484.5 451.158L245.5 196.158L444 463.5L222.805 644.772Z" fill="#0ea5e9" />
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600"><b>Warmbly</b> ("we", "us", "our") is operated by <b>Mindroot Ltd</b>. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal information when you use our website <a href="https://warmbly.com" class="text-sky-600 hover:underline">warmbly.com</a> and associated services (the "Services").
                By accessing or using our Services, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-5">At Mindroot Ltd, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data in accordance with the UK General Data Protection Regulation (UK GDPR), the Data Protection Act 2018, and applicable international data protection laws. Warmbly is available worldwide, and we ensure compliance with data protection standards globally.</p>
            <hr class="my-10 text-gray-200"/>
            <h2 class="text-gray-800 mb-9 text-2xl font-bold">1. Who We Are</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-10">
                We are Mindroot Ltd, a company registered in England and Wales with registration number 16543299 and registered office at 71-75 Shelton Street, London, England, WC2H 9JQ. We are registered with the Information Commissioner's Office (ICO) with registration number "Pending". You can contact us at team@warmbly.com.
            </p>
            <h2 class="text-gray-800 mb-9 text-2xl font-bold">2. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-10">
                <b>a) Account Information</b><br/><br/>

                When you create an account, we collect only the minimum necessary information:<br/>
                    •	Email address<br/>
                    •	Password<br/>
                    • Timestamps<br/><br/>

                Passwords are hashed securely using Argon2 before storing in our database to protect your credentials.<br/><br/>

                <b>b) Mailbox Data</b><br/><br/>

                If you connect mailboxes to our Services, any sensitive data associated with those mailboxes is stored in encrypted form to ensure confidentiality and security.<br/><br/>

                <b>c) No Additional Tracking</b><br/><br/>

                We do not store IP addresses, device information, cookies, or any other tracking data.
            </p>
            <h2 class="text-gray-800 mb-9 text-2xl font-bold">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-10">We use your information solely for:<br/>
                    •	Providing and maintaining the Services<br/>
                    •	Authenticating users and securing accounts<br/>
                    •	Communicating important updates and support messages<br/>
                    •	Improving and developing new features<br/>
                    •	Ensuring compliance with legal obligations<br/><br/>

                We do not collect or process any personal data beyond what is strictly necessary for the operation of the Services.</p>
            <h2 class="text-gray-800 mb-9 text-2xl font-bold">4. Data Storage and Security</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-10">
                	•	All user data is stored on Amazon Web Services (AWS) infrastructure, specifically using Amazon RDS for PostgreSQL databases.<br/>
                    •	Passwords are hashed with Argon2 algorithm before storage.<br/>
                    •	Sensitive mailbox data is stored encrypted at rest using industry-standard encryption methods.<br/>
                    •	We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to safeguard your data against unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction.
            </p>
            <h2 class="text-gray-800 mb-9 text-2xl font-bold">5. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-10">We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share data only when required by law or to protect our rights and property.</p>
            <h2 class="text-gray-800 mb-9 text-2xl font-bold">6. Your Rights</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-10">Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have rights regarding your personal data, including:<br/>
                    •	Access to your data<br/>
                    •	Rectification of inaccurate data<br/>
                    •	Deletion of your data ("right to be forgotten")<br/>
                    •	Restriction of processing<br/>
                    •	Data portability<br/><br/>

                To exercise these rights, please contact us at support@warmbly.com.</p>
            <h2 class="text-gray-800 mb-9 text-2xl font-bold">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-10">Our Services are not directed to children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>
            <h2 class="text-gray-800 mb-9 text-2xl font-bold">8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-10">
                We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the new policy on our website. Continued use of the Services after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
            </p>
            <h2 class="text-gray-800 mb-9 text-2xl font-bold">9. Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-10">
                For questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, contact us at <b>team@warmbly.com</b> or write to 71-75 Shelton Street, London, England, WC2H 9JQ.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
